<br>
Rogues aren't the top of the foodchain in PvP right now, in my opinion. Others disagree with me and claim that rogues are arguably the strongest PvP class out there. But that doesn't change my view, that melee damage / archery / dmg shields should be nerfed in PvP, as an overall balance improvement. <br>
